translated: Mellander, Jolian Axel Leionand, clergyman, contract priest, Hediås, born on August 4, 1889 in Björike village, ÄjUvisb. Married on August 21 to Siigrd'd LeontoTia Angustrd GnoirtTS. Children: Gerid born in 1922, Nddls in 1924, Banbro in 1928, Jarl and Stefani in 1930, Biriiita in 1934. Completed studies in 1908, theological degree in 1909, theological seminary in 1913. Assistant pastor in Bredared parish from 1916-1919, second parish priest in Siamiariiinterlnemm. in Uppis. from 1919-1925, clergyman in Ryda parish from 1925. Chairman of the Ryda, Naums, and S. Kedums church councils, member of the Ryda (church assembly and parish council), librarian, diakonia society, representative for the county temperance union in Ryda, inspector for Vara secondary school, member of the board of Swedish Church Mission.
